	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Guy, the guys behind Scott Pilgrim VS The World are making a new game called Mercenary Kings and I think that more people should know about this effort. I recommend to everyone that enjoyed Scott Pilgrim VS The World to go check it out as it look really awesome. If the game get funded properly, we might see even cooler feature added like online play and more. I think that crowd-funding could change the way video game are developed and it might be the key to have really original and cool innovative game that would never be made otherwise. So instead of funding stupid stuff like the Cheetahman 2 cart reproduction, I suggest looking at Mercenary King, Castle Story, Shadowrun and all the other nice project on kickstarter. Might not be the worst 15$ you ever spent on a game, plus your helping build a new way of publishing game!<br /><br /><a href="http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/322438897/mercenary-kings" class="postlink">http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/322438897/mercenary-kings</a>

		

